{"author":{"id":"977fec8a59c245f25e0e700fa290ef50836c624572869487e9e47fedc85061ee"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1456340289,"nonce":"rDrilkUvb4fWIC31liJOrsh78QI=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDE4ODQwNTM4Nw==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/614#issuecomment-188405387"},"message":"We can get a nice speedup by not compressing in the view, but in the sort step, as point out in `samtools view --help`:\n\n```\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam | samtools view -bS - | samtools sort - -@1 -o hsbam \u003e standard.bam\n\nreal    0m1.274s\nuser    0m1.292s\nsys 0m0.036s\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam | samtools view -u - | samtools sort - -@1 -l 6 -o hsbam \u003e l6.bam\n\nreal    0m0.856s\nuser    0m0.840s\nsys 0m0.036s\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ ls -l\ntotal 1409716\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 marius marius   19648618 févr. 24 19:03 100k.sam\n-rw-r----- 1 marius marius 1418464214 févr. 24 19:02 Galaxy392-[HISAT2_on_data_5_and_data_388].bam\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 marius marius    2708323 févr. 24 19:31 l6.bam\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 marius marius    2708323 févr. 24 19:30 standard.bam\n```\n\nCompressing with 2 threads also gives a speedup:\n\n```\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam | samtools view -u - | samtools sort - -@2 -l 6 -o hsbam \u003e l6.bam\n\nreal    0m0.550s\nuser    0m0.776s\nsys 0m0.064s\n```\n\nMore than that doesn't really help:\n\n```\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam | samtools view -u - | samtools sort - -@3 -l 6 -o hsbam \u003e l6.bam\n\nreal    0m0.523s\nuser    0m0.856s\nsys 0m0.056s\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam | samtools view -u - | samtools sort - -@4 -l 6 -o hsbam \u003e l6.bam\n\nreal    0m0.501s\nuser    0m0.900s\nsys 0m0.072s\n\n```\n\nWe can also completely skip the view:\n\n```\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam  | samtools sort - -@2 -l 6 -o hsbam \u003e l6.bam\n\nreal    0m0.524s\nuser    0m0.732s\nsys 0m0.028s\n\n(.venv)marius@iMac-ubuntu:~/src/samtools_sambamba_comp$ time cat 100k.sam  | samtools sort - -@4 -l 6 -o hsbam \u003e l6.bam\n\nreal    0m0.420s\nuser    0m0.828s\nsys 0m0.048s\n\n```\n\nI didn't get sambamba to work with piped sam input, I'm not sure this is a supported pattern,\nbut if anyone know how to do this I'd be interested to compare.\n\nLet's see how that translates into the hisat2 wrapper. I guess.","files":null}]}